channel.title: Daylight Moon - Alyen [Trance], [Rating Poll], [SC]
channel.description:
Hey guys, wanted to try something that I might start using when posting tracks(in moderation). The poll below is scaled from 1(garbage)-10(Amazing). I’ve made the poll anonymous to encourage voters to vote honestly. This will also serve as data for future community projects that I wish to put together. Note that only the even numbers have descriptions, but all are valid voting options.
**How would you rate this track?** https://soundcloud.com/alyen-musyc/daylight-moon [poll min=1 max=10] * 10.) I love it, favorite for me * 9.) * 8.) It’s good and I can see myself listening again * 7.) * 6.) Decent * 5.) * 4.) There were good ideas in it * 3.) * 2.) I cannot listen to all it * 1.) [/poll]

item.title: Daylight Moon - Alyen [Trance], [Rating Poll], [SC]
item.dc:creator: iammane
item.description:
I dig it. Trance isn’t really my bag, I do like the filtered bass and the piano work. Great kick very thick. The riser is a little abrasive but it’s at least unique. Maybe if it was less loud it would help? Or had more of the high freq filtered out.

That’s about all I got. Good melodies for sure though, very trance-y to my untrained ears
